==Chinese==
===Mandarin===
[[Pinyin]]: hăo mă bù chī huítóu căo
===Etymology===
Literally: A good horse does not look back to eat grass.
===Proverb===
'''[[好]][[馬]][[不]][[吃]][[回頭]][[草]]'''
# A smart person does not dwell on past actions.
===Alternate forms===
[[好马不吃回头草]] ([[Simplified Chinese]])
